metadata.name: A Future Beyond The Stars Pt. 1
metadata.description:
"As we gaze to the stars, may our eyes rest upon a brighter future - one where we want not the posessions of our fellow man, and our souls are free to explore the great mystery that is our universe. 
Let this piece stare into you as you would a night sky."

The work is part of an AI Art Contest organized by Claire Silver.
Created with Midjourney, Adobe Photoshop & Clip Studio Paint.
#ClaireAIContest
